text: public int addNumbers(int a, int b) { return a + b; }
public int multiplyNumbers(int a, int b) { return a * b; }
public void printMax(int a, int b) { System.out.println(Math.max(a, b)); }
public int subtractNumbers(int a, int b) { return a - b; }
public void printMin(int a, int b) { System.out.println(Math.min(a, b)); }
public long largeMultiplication(int a, int b) { return (long) a * b; }
public double calculateArea(double length, double width) { return length * width; }
public int increment(int a) { return a + 1; }
public int decrement(int a) { return a - 1; }
